window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>What happens in Vegas stays in Vegas . . .</p> <p>That's true unless your new husband—who is much younger than you by the way—doesn't actually want a divorce when you both sober up.</p> <p>Or, of course, if you get pregnant—the last thing you need right after becoming the new GM to a failing pro hockey team.</p> <p>I guess you could say this year won't be easy.</p> <p>Especially for me, the owner.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
